external_knowledge:
- 'Long' calls refer to calls lasting more than 5 minutes (300 seconds); 
- 'Successful' calls are those with a call outcome ID of 1; 
- 'Active' callers and receivers are those who registered in 2023; 
- 'Exported' calls are those with an export record in 2023; 
- 'Customer support' calls have a call purpose ID of 1.

sql:
SELECT AVG(c.duration) AS average_call_duration
FROM calls c
WHERE c.caller_id = 0 AND c.call_start_time LIKE '%2023-05-02%';

SELECT COUNT(*) 
FROM call_tags 
WHERE created_by = 'Admin User';

SELECT SUM(LENGTH(caller_phone)) AS total_digits
FROM callers
WHERE status = 'active';

SELECT COUNT(*)
FROM callers
WHERE status = 'active';
